<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hu">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Skyhigh AI | Csúcstechnológia</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Orbitron:wght@900&display=swap');
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #000; color: #fff; }
        .font-robot { font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif; }
        .bento-card { background: #0a0a0a; border: 1px solid #1a1a1a; border-radius: 28px; }
        .purple-glow { color: #a855f7; text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.4); }
        .nav-pill { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: #555; transition: 0.3s; }
        .active-pill { color: #a855f7; border-bottom: 2px solid #a855f7; padding-bottom: 4px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="pb-20">

    <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-black/90 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-white/5 px-6 py-4">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-5">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-robot text-purple-500 text-xl"></i>
                    <span class="font-robot text-lg tracking-tighter uppercase italic">Skyhigh<span class="text-green-500">.Ai</span></span>
                </div>
                <a href="/regisztracio" class="bg-white text-black text-[10px] font-black px-5 py-2 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest shadow-lg">Belépés</a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-center gap-8 border-t border-white/5 pt-4">
                <a href="/" class="nav-pill">Home</a>
                <a href="/technologia" class="nav-pill active-pill">Technológia</a>
                <a href="/halozat" class="nav-pill">Hálózat</a>
                <a href="/strategia" class="nav-pill">Stratégia</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="pt-48 pb-16 px-8 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none mb-8">
            Kvantum Sebesség. <br> <span class="purple-glow italic text-5xl md:text-6xl">Matematikai Siker.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-12">
            A Skyhigh AI a világ egyik leggyorsabb <br> sport-analitikai motorja.
        </p>
    </header>

    <section class="px-6 space-y-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bento-card p-10 border-l-4 border-purple-500">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black uppercase italic mb-4">Éles Matematikai Analízis</h3>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed uppercase font-bold">
                A robotunk <span class="text-white">miliszekundumok alatt</span> futtatja le a világ összes odds-változását. Nem tippel, hanem kiszámolja a legfrissebb információk alapján a győzelmi esélyeket. Ez a csúcstechnológia tesz Téged profi sportfogadóvá.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bento-card p-6 text-center">
                <i class="fas fa-bolt text-yellow-500 text-xl mb-3"></i>
                <h5 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase">Gyorsaság</h5>
                <p class="text-[8px] text-zinc-600 uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter">Adatfeldolgozás < 1.0s</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-card p-6 text-center">
                <i class="fas fa-brain text-purple-500 text-xl mb-3"></i>
                <h5 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase">AI Memória</h5>
                <p class="text-[8px] text-zinc-600 uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter">365 napos tőkekövetés</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-card p-6 text-center">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-green-500 text-xl mb-3"></i>
                <h5 class="text-[10px] font-black uppercase">Biztonság</h5>
                <p class="text-[8px] text-zinc-600 uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter">Matematikai tőkevédelem</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>